# 📣 Distribution Kit

> **Generated**: [Date and time]  
> **Agent**: Content Optimizer  
> This file is refreshed each session with current distribution priorities.
> Check `agent-log.md` PART 9 for distribution history and insights.

---

## How This Works

1. **Agent audits** all content and identifies high-potential posts
2. **Agent generates** copy-pasteable content for each platform
3. **You post** to the platforms when ready
4. **Next session**, tell the agent the links so it can track results

---

