## 📝 After You Post

Tell the agent at next session:

> "Posted [post name] to [platform] — [link]"

Examples:
- "Posted ML Year in Review to Twitter — https://x.com/samim/status/123456"
- "Posted Brain Wave Engine to HN — https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=789"

The agent will:
1. Log it in `agent-log.md` PART 9
2. Set a reminder to check referrer data in 7 days
3. Update distribution insights with learnings

