| Platform | Best Times | Notes |
|----------|------------|-------|
| Twitter | [Based on audience analysis] | Threads get more engagement than single tweets |
| Hacker News | Weekday mornings US (9am-11am EST) | Avoid weekends |
| Reddit | Varies by sub | Check when each sub is most active |
| LinkedIn | Tue-Thu mornings | Business hours |

